'''萨尔曼·阿敏·可汗'''（{{lang-bn|সালমান খান}}，{{lang-en|Salman Amin Khan}}，{{bd|1976年|10月11日||catIdx=Khan, Salman}}），暱稱'''萨尔·可汗'''（{{lang|en|Sal Khan}}），生於美國路易斯安納州{{link-en|梅泰理|Metairie, Louisiana}}，科技教育實踐家，以及免費網上教育平台及非營利機構[[可汗學院|可汗學院]]的創辦人。他制作了超過4,700個主要教授[[數學|數學]]和[[科學|科學]]的視頻並將其上傳到網上。由於他的教學方法簡單易明，影片一直大受歡迎。直至2012年6月30日，他在[[YouTube|YouTube]]的頻道已經吸引了超過2億1千萬人次觀看<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/user/khanacademy |title=可汗學院 官方YouTube頻道 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |language=en }}</ref>。美國[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]並推選可汗為2012年度的[[時代百大人物|時代百大人物]]之一<ref>{{cite news|title=Salman Khan - Time 100|url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2111975_2111976_2111942,00.html|accessdate=2012-06-30|newspaper=[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]|date=2012-04-18|language=en|archive-date=2013-05-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GIG1Wtft?url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2111975_2111976_2111942,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==早期生活及學歷==
可汗出生於美國[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]的[[新奧爾良|新奧爾良]]，他的父親來自[[孟加拉|孟加拉]]的[[巴里薩爾|巴里薩爾]]，而他母親來自[[印度|印度]]的[[加爾各答|加爾各答]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.khanacademy.org/about/faq#where-from |title=可汗學院網站 常見問題頁 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |language=en |archive-date=2011-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103050019/http://www.khanacademy.org/about/faq#where-from |dead-url=no }}</ref>可汗的母親為了獨力養大他，在新奧爾良有過一系列不同的工作和生計。<ref>{{cite news |author=Somini Sengupta |title=Online Learning, Personalized |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/05/technology/khan-academy-blends-its-youtube-approach-with-classrooms.html?_r=2&hpw |publisher=紐約時報 |date=2011-12-04 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |language=en |quote=Mr. Khan grew up in a suburb of New Orleans, where his mother, who is from Bangladesh, raised him on her own by cobbling together a series of jobs and businesses. }}</ref>可汗曾就讀於公共學校，他對此有這樣的回憶：「一些同學剛剛從監獄出來，其他的則往最好的大學進發。」他現在擁有多個學位，包括來自[[麻省理工學院|麻省理工學院]]的數學理學士、電子工程及電腦科學理學士、以及電子工程及電腦科學碩士，另他亦擭得[[哈佛大學商學院|哈佛大學商學院]]頒發的工商管理碩士。<ref name="GatesFavorite">{{cite news |last=Kaplan |first=David A. |url=http://money.cnn.com/2010/08/23/technology/sal_khan_academy.fortune/index.htm |title=Sal Khan: Bill Gates' favorite teacher |publisher=Money.cnn.com |date=2010-08-24 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |archive-date=2018-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180628212411/http://money.cnn.com/2010/08/23/technology/sal_khan_academy.fortune/index.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Posted |url=http://mixergy.com/salman-khan-academy-interview/ |title=How Khan Academy Is Changing Education With Videos Made In A Closet – with Salman Khan |publisher=Mixergy.com |date=2010-06-28 |accessdate=2010-08-26 |language=en |archive-date=2014-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209192955/http://mixergy.com/salman-khan-academy-interview/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==事業==
在2010前，他是一名[[對沖基金|-{zh-cn:对冲基金;zh-tw:避險基金;zh-hk:對沖基金;}-]]的[[金融分析師|分析員]]。<ref name="colbertnation.com">{{cite video |people=Stephen Colbert (Host) |year=2011 |title=The Colbert Report |url=http://www.colbertnation.com/the-colbert-report-videos/388279/june-02-2011/salman-khan |language=en |publisher=Colbert Nation |accessdate=2012-06-30 |archive-date=2013-05-01 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GIG29nK2?url=http://www.colbertnation.com/the-colbert-report-videos/388279/june-02-2011/salman-khan |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="http://chronicle.com">{{cite web |last=Kowarski |first=Ilana |url=http://chronicle.com/article/A-Self-Appointed-Teacher-Runs/65793/ |title=College 2.0: A Self-Appointed Teacher Runs a One-Man 'Academy' on YouTube - Technology - The Chronicle of Higher Education |publisher=Chronicle.com |date=2010-06-06 |accessdate=2010-08-26 |archive-date=2016-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160606062613/http://chronicle.com/article/A-Self-Appointed-Teacher-Runs/65793/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===可汗學院===
{{Main |可汗學院}}
2004年底，可汗開始使用[[雅虎|雅虎]]的Doodle Notepad來教授表妹數學。<ref name="Khan Academy">{{cite video |year=2011 |title=Salman Khan: Let's use video to reinvent education |url=http://www.ted.com/talks/salman_khan_let_s_use_video_to_reinvent_education.html |language=en |trans_title=Salman Khan：影片能改變教育 |publisher=TED |accessdate=2012-06-30 |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222022519/http://www.ted.com/talks/salman_khan_let_s_use_video_to_reinvent_education.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>當其他親戚朋友開始找他幫忙補習時，他決定錄製一些教學視頻並將其上傳到YouTube，以便學生使用。<ref name="youtube1">{{cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/user/khanacademy |title=khanacademy |publisher=YouTube |date=2006-11-16 |accessdate=2010-06-30}}</ref>他的視頻迅速受到廣泛歡迎。於是，他在2009年辭去了分析員的工作，全心投入於教學視頻的製作。<ref name="http://chronicle.com" />

可汗這樣形容他的使命：「要加快不同年紀學生的學習步伐。有着這樣的想法，我們希望向任何人分享對他們有用的材料。」他亦計劃增加如[[英國文學|英國文學]]等的題材來擴展他這所「免費學校」。而[[非洲|非洲]]和[[亞洲|亞洲]]的一些偏遠地區亦已開始使用可汗的影片作教授用途。當談及自己的動機，可汗說：
<blockquote>「當我用如此少的努力便能把知識賦予如此多的人時，我實在想不到還能怎樣更善用時間。」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.sfgate.com/2009-12-14/business/17224380_1_youtube-videos-vocabulary-tests |title=Salman Khan, math master of the Internet - SFGate |publisher=Articles.sfgate.com |date=2009-12-14 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |first=James |last=Temple |quote=With so little effort on my own part, I can empower an unlimited amount of people for all time," Khan, 33, said. "I can't imagine a better use of my time. |language=en |archive-date=2010-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610104357/http://articles.sfgate.com/2009-12-14/business/17224380_1_youtube-videos-vocabulary-tests |dead-url=no }}</ref></blockquote>

==備受肯定==
包括[[CNN|CNN]]<ref>{{cite video | url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ZAlj2gu0eM | title=CNN: Understanding the Crisis | medium=YouTube | publisher=khanacademy | accessdate=2012-06-30 |language=en }}</ref>、[[全國公共廣播電台|全國公共廣播電台]]<ref>{{cite web |author=All Things Considered |url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=121978193 |title=Ex-Hedge Fund Analyst Finds Calling On YouTube |publisher=NPR |date=2009-12-28 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |language=en |archive-date=2017-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027074632/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=121978193 |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[公共電視網|公共電視網]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pbs.org/newshour/bb/north_america/jan-june10/khan_02-22.html |title=Math Wiz Adds Web Tools to Take Education to New Limits |publisher=PBS |date=2010-02-22 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |archiveurl=http://wingate-goodpeopleaward.blogspot.hk/2010/02/salman-khan-education-revolutionary.html |archivedate=2010-02-23 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Spencer Michels |url=http://www.pbs.org/newshour/rundown/2010/02/khan-academy-how-to-calculate-the-unemployment-rate.html |title=Khan Academy: How to Calculate the Unemployment Rate | The Rundown News Blog | PBS NewsHour |publisher=PBS |date=2010-02-22 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |language=en |archive-date=2011-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110119111707/http://www.pbs.org/newshour/rundown/2010/02/khan-academy-how-to-calculate-the-unemployment-rate.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ethicsandentrepreneurship.org/20100608/online-education-entrepreneur-salman-khan/ |title=Online Education Entrepreneur: Salman Khan » Center for Ethics and Entrepreneurship |publisher=Ethicsandentrepreneurship.org |date=2010-06-08 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027025906/http://www.ethicsandentrepreneurship.org/20100608/online-education-entrepreneur-salman-khan/ |archive-date=2017-10-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>在內的多個美國傳媒曾以薩爾曼·可汗的作專題報導。<ref name="colbertnation.com"/>於2009年，可汗學院榮獲[[微軟|微軟]]科技教育獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://thetechawards.thetech.org/laureate/archive/2009 |title=The Tech Awards - Technology Benefiting Humanity |publisher=The Tech Awards |accessdate=2012-06-30 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120715144932/http://thetechawards.thetech.org/laureate/archive/2009 |archivedate=2012-07-15 }}</ref>。於2010年，[[Google|Google]]向可汗學院捐款二百萬元美金來維持學院製作更多課程，並把核心內容翻譯至世界上各種被廣泛使用的語言<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.google.com/onceuponatime/project10tothe100/ |title=Project 10 to the 100 |work=Project 10 to the 100 |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |year=2010 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |language=en |archive-date=2012-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121126052844/http://www.google.com/onceuponatime/project10tothe100/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

